1310-73-2



Sodium Lauryl Sulfate

plant-derived cleaning ingredient
provides cleaning and foaming
68585-47-7



Sodium Methyl 2-Sulfolaurate

readily biodegradable surfactant with viscosity modifying characteristics from coconut
provides foaming and cleaning power
149458-07-1



Sodium Methyl Cocoyl Taurate

very mild surfactant (surface active agent)
foams and cleanses without stripping away natural oils from skin
61791-42-2



Sodium Polyacrylate

acrylic polymer
disperses food particles and helps to prevent their redeposition on surfaces
68479-09-4



Sodium Silicate

natural mineral
disperses grease and food deposits into small, suspended particles that easily rinse away
1344-09-8



Sodium Sulfate

mineral salt
softens water to boost cleaning performance
7757-82-6



Sorbitol

natural vegetable sugar
keeps detergent intact from temperature changes during shipping
50-70-4



Stearic Acid

fatty acid salt
emulsifies and solubilizes for homogenous solutions
57-11-4




Subtilisin (Protease) Enzyme Blend

enzyme from biofermentation reaction
removes protein stains and helps the detergent ingredients clean even better
9014-01-1, 57-55-6, 141-53-7



Tetrasodium Etidronate

chelating agent to adjust pH
converts oils into solid soap
3794-83-0



Tetrasodium Glutamate Diacetate

non-EDTA chelating agent
softens water to boost cleaning performance
5198-21-6



Thuja Occidentalis (Cedar) Leaf Oil

natural essential oil
provides fragrance and cleaning efficacy
8007-20-3



Titanium Dioxide

natural mineral
provides whiteness and opacity to soap bar
13463-67-7



Trideceth-9

emulsifier that makes oils compatible with water
blends essential oils and fragrance evenly into the formula
69011-36-5



Vegetable Oils

natural palm and coconut oils
moisturizes and soothes skin
68956-68-3



Vegetable Wax Base

renewable wax from a mix of soy and corn ingredients
earth-friendly wax that burns cleanly, delivers fragrance and ambiance
8016-70-4, 8015-86-9



Vetiveria Zizanioides (Vetiver) Oil

natural essential oil
provides fragrance
8016-96-4



Water

deionized/demineralized water that has passed through filters to remove minerals
holds all ingredients together in solution
7732-18-5



Xanthan Gum

plant-derived polysaccharide from biofermentation process
thickens product so it clings to the side of the bowl to clean better
11138-66-2



Zingiber Officinale (Ginger) Root Oil

natural essential oil
provides fragrance
8007-08-7










 










